    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "A shampoo bar works on the same ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "saponification",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "glossaryTooltip",
                "attrs": {
                  "termSlug": "saponification"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " chemistry as skin soap but with two key differences: a high proportion of ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "lauric acid",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "glossaryTooltip",
                "attrs": {
                  "termSlug": "lauric-acid"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " oils for lather, and a 0% ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "superfat",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "glossaryTooltip",
                "attrs": {
                  "termSlug": "superfat"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " to prevent the waxy coating that ruins the experience. Argan sits at 10% of the oil weight, enough to add its renowned oleic acid shine without tipping the bar into conditioner territory. Always follow with an ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "apple cider vinegar rinse",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "glossaryTooltip",
                "attrs": {
                  "termSlug": "acv-rinse"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " (1 tablespoon ACV in 250 ml water) to close the cuticle and restore pH. Shelf life is 2 years from the cure date.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Before you begin"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "This recipe uses sodium hydroxide. Read and follow the ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "working-with-lye-safely",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "techniqueLink",
                "attrs": {
                  "techniqueSlug": "working-with-lye-safely"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " technique. Wear protective goggles and gloves throughout. Pour lye into water, never water into lye.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Ingredients"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "ingredientsList",
        "attrs": {
          "defaultServings": 1,
          "items": [
            {
              "ingredientSlug": "coconut-oil",
              "amount": 400,
              "unit": "g",
              "isOptional": false,
              "prepNote": "40% of oil weight; primary lather oil"
            },
            {
              "ingredientSlug": "castor-oil",
              "amount": 300,
              "unit": "g",
              "isOptional": false,
              "prepNote": "30% of oil weight; conditioning lather"
            },
            {
              "ingredientSlug": "olive-oil",
              "amount": 200,
              "unit": "g",
              "isOptional": false,
              "prepNote": "20% of oil weight"
            },
            {
              "ingredientSlug": "argan-oil",
              "amount": 100,
              "unit": "g",
              "isOptional": false,
              "prepNote": "10% of oil weight"
            },
            {
              "ingredientSlug": "sodium-hydroxide",
              "amount": 153,
              "unit": "g",
              "isOptional": false,
